    "Id": "763415",
    "ThreadId": "308163",
    "Html": "<p>Not sure about WPF5 but Prism 4.1 (for Silverlight 5) will be coming out soon, and the next big target will be 4.5 to match up with the .NET framework.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<blockquote style=\"border: solid .1em #ccc; font-style: italic; margin: .25em 1em 0 1em; padding: 0 .25em 0 .25em;\">\r\n<h3>Future Releases</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Prism 4.1 targetting Silverlight 5. Go <a href=\"http://blogs.msdn.com/b/blaine/archive/2011/12/14/starting-work-on-prism-4-1.aspx\"> here </a>to learn about future releases. </li>\r\n<li>Prism 4.5 targetting .NET 4.5. </li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<p>From above link two of the latest posts from a Prism developer.</p>\r\n<blockquote style=\"border: solid .1em #ccc; font-style: italic; margin: .25em 1em 0 1em; padding: 0 .25em 0 .25em;\">\r\n<p><span class=\"profile-usercard-hover\"><span class=\"user-name\"><a href=\"http://blogs.msdn.com/66316/ProfileUrlRedirect.ashx\">bmw1122 </a> </span> </span></p>\r\n<div class=\"post-date\"><span class=\"value\">1 Feb 2012 12:12 PM</span></div>\r\n<p><a style=\"padding-left: 5px;\" name=\"10262932\" href=\"http://blogs.msdn.com/b/blaine/archive/2011/12/14/starting-work-on-prism-4-1.aspx#10262932\">#</a></p>\r\n<div class=\"post-content user-defined-markup\">\r\n<p>Prism  4.1 will out be next week. We had some delays in getting our test team  to test the bits which is why it is not out yet. We are going through  our final tests this week and will publish it next week. Sorry about the  delays.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<p>...</p>\r\n<blockquote style=\"border: solid .1em #ccc; font-style: italic; margin: .25em 1em 0 1em; padding: 0 .25em 0 .25em;\">\r\n<p><span class=\"profile-usercard-hover\"><span class=\"user-name\"><a href=\"http://blogs.msdn.com/66316/ProfileUrlRedirect.ashx\">bmw1122 </a> </span> </span></p>\r\n<div class=\"post-date\"><span class=\"value\">9 Feb 2012 11:46 AM</span></div>\r\n<p><a style=\"padding-left: 5px;\" name=\"10266093\" href=\"http://blogs.msdn.com/b/blaine/archive/2011/12/14/starting-work-on-prism-4-1.aspx#10266093\">#</a></p>\r\n<div class=\"post-content user-defined-markup\">\r\n<p>We are not quite done. I will make a post on my blog when it is published.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</blockquote>",
